OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 05 JUL
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1954FThe first TV news programme airs
OL,7,Fon BBC TV. Richard Baker introduces the
OL,8,Ffirst bulletin, BBC News and Newsreel
OL,9,F(22 minutes long), at 7pm, with the
OL,10,Ffollowing words: "Here is an
OL,11,Fillustrated summary of the news. It
OL,12,Fwill be followed by the latest film of
OL,13,Fevents and happenings at home and
OL,14,Fabroad." John Snagge and Andrew
OL,15,FTimothy's voices were then heard
OL,16,Freading the news behind film, stills
OL,17,Fand captions from the studios at
OL,18,FAlexandra Palace.
OL,19,
OL,20,
OL,21,
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
